data.description: Custom built retreat nestled at the base of the Rincon Mountains. Got horses? Property is 4.22 acres and is surrounded by beautiful open space. With 4 spacious bedrooms and 4 bathrooms, this Desert Gem boasts vaulted ceilings with wood beams, recessed lighting, ceiling fans, Alder doors and Alder cabinets throughout! Travertine flooring in all living areas and berber carpeting in the bedrooms. Spacious kitchen w/ granite countertops, prestige travertine backsplash, dual sinks, new upgraded appliances and fixtures, and AMAZING mountain views through picture window!  Master bath w/ dual sinks, jacuzzi tub, custom travertine walk-in shower w/ dual shower heads. Extended covered back patio with ceiling fans for outside entertaining and great mountain and sunset views! Large three car garage with plenty of shelving for added storage. A true must see! New Patio roof, new water softer/filtration RO system, new interior paint, new LED lighting throughout, new faucets, Minks Aire fans and chandeliers, new shed, ring security with cameras,  and New AC zone control and digital thermostats.
